9951d978bbabcea3030ae5ca0dd2bb80f","tid":2492794,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"豬喺舊約聖經係不潔 其實唔係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a697818918758562eee73370e7a6bee5fe3f725","tid":2492794,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e88e036e35e9cbe2117dc406e4f7f41767a6f4e","tid":2492794,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0530f56c3fe0cf80ff016dc7aef535d4e5918fc6","tid":2492794,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e861f873bcb7588948a5048504a60d10e11e230","tid":2492794,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"西班牙黑毛豬, 雖然唔係日本"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"咁點解冇人食豬刺身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"【now新聞台】日本人喜歡吃刺身，但日本共同社報道，日本厚生勞動省下令，由下月中起，所有餐廳一律不准供應豬肝和豬肉刺身，以減低食物中毒的機會。<br />\n<br />\n厚生勞動省指豬肉和豬肝可能帶有可致命的戊型肝炎病毒，而且豬肝表面可能有沙門氏菌等惡菌，容易引致食物中毒。厚生勞動省因而決定修改食品衛生法，規定所有餐廳處理豬肝時，要以攝氏63度加熱30分鐘以上。若違例，餐廳東主可能面臨兩年以下的有期徒刑，或罰款200萬日圓，折合約12萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n早在2011年，日本曾經爆發大規模食物中毒，導致5人死亡，180人不適，病人全在同一間餐廳吃過生牛肉後發病。因此，當局在三年前收緊有關法例，禁止餐廳供應牛肝刺身。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:37:35.000Z","msg":"咁其實鵝肝雞肉都有惡菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4e98701a7441972c51e408b363d020f8ed2ebf","tid":2492794,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"有蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344abe4e01374400f4ad0d3c323d26418a66a568","tid":2492794,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7c6990a95f937dbf84ccf6d1a51fa12855cc0c","t